data.description: 2.9% assumable loan! 2020 Roof! PAID OFF SOLAR! 4/2/2 with french doors to den/office area, CBS POOL home NO HOA. 1/3 acre fenced yard with mature trees, plantings and eloquent palm trees that back to a preserve for privacy.  Perfect 14x28 salt water pool with covered & screened in patio area. New luxury vinyl flooring throughout with fresh paint on interior & exterior. Beautiful new barn doors in master bedroom. Bright & updated kitchen showcasing quartz counters, large island and open floor plan make gatherings a bliss. 2 car garage has a mini split & insulated garage door which cools in just minutes for a gym or work space. Whole house surge protector professionally installed with TESLA charger and solar panels make for very low electric bills. ADA features throughout.
